</group>

textfsm_template:
Value FEATURE (\S+)
Value LICENSE_TYPE (\S+)
Value STATE (.+)
Value EXPIRY_DATE (\S+)

Start
  ^Feature\s+:\s+${FEATURE}\s*$$
  ^License\s+Type\s+:\s+${LICENSE_TYPE}\s*$$
  ^State\s+:\s+${STATE}\s*$$
  ^Expiry\s+Date\s+:\s+${EXPIRY_DATE}\s*$$ -> Record
